  "prompt_text": "Design an API for a task management application. Specify endpoints, methods, and data formats.",
  "response_text": "**Task Management API Design**\n\n**Endpoints**\n\n### User Endpoints\n\n#### 1. User Registration\n- **POST /users**\n  - Request Body: `{\"username\": string, \"email\": string, \"password\": string}`\n  - Response: `{\"id\": integer, \"username\": string, \"email\": string}`\n\n#### 2. User Login\n- **POST /users/login**\n  - Request Body: `{\"username\": string, \"password\": string}`\n  - Response: `{\"token\": string, \"username\": string, \"email\": string}`\n\n#### 3. User Profile\n- **GET /users/{id}**\n  - Response: `{\"id\": integer, \"username\": string, \"email\": string, \"tasks\": [task object]}`\n\n### Task Endpoints\n\n#### 1. Create Task\n- **POST /tasks**\n  - Request Body: `{\"title\": string, \"description\": string, \"due_date\": date, \"status\": string}`\n  - Response: `{\"id\": integer, \"title\": string, \"description\": string, \"due_date\": date, \"status\": string}`\n\n#### 2. Get Tasks\n- **GET /tasks**\n  - Query Parameters: `status=string, due_date=date`\n  - Response: `[task object]`\n\n#### 3. Get Task\n- **GET /tasks/{id}**\n  - Response: `{\"id\": integer, \"title\": string, \"description\": string, \"due_date\": date, \"status\": string}`\n\n#### 4. Update Task\n- **PUT /tasks/{id}**\n  - Request Body: `{\"title\": string, \"description\": string, \"due_date\": date, \"status\": string}`\n  - Response: `{\"id\": integer, \"title\": string, \"description\": string, \"due_date\": date, \"status\": string}`\n\n#### 5. Delete Task\n- **DELETE /tasks/{id}**\n  - Response: `{\"message\": string}`\n\n### Task Status Endpoints\n\n#### 1. Update Task Status\n- **PATCH /tasks/{id}/status**\n  - Request Body: `{\"status\": string}`\n  - Response: `{\"id\": integer, \"title\": string, \"description\": string, \"due_date\": date, \"status\": string}`\n\n### Task List Endpoints\n\n#### 1. Create Task List\n- **POST /task_lists**\n  - Request Body: `{\"title\": string, \"description\": string}`\n  - Response: `{\"id\": integer, \"title\": string, \"description\": string}`\n\n#### 2. Get Task List\n- **GET /task_lists/{id}**\n  - Response: `{\"id\": integer, \"title\": string, \"description\": string, \"tasks\": [task object]}`\n\n",
